OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1775315485
OL,3,CHusband, 51, jailed for wife's murder
OL,4,Cafter she initiated divorce proceedings
OL,6,FA coercive husband has been jailed for
OL,7,Flife for stabbing and strangling his
OL,8,Fwife to death weeks after she
OL,9,Finitiated divorce proceedings.
OL,11,FHarminder Mattu, 51, of Swan Crescent,
OL,12,FOldbury, was handed a minimum term of
OL,13,F18 years after Judge John Butterfield
OL,14,FKC ruled that he intended to kill
OL,15,FParamjit Kaur on the evening of 30
OL,16,FMarch 2025.
OL,18,FThe court heard how Mattu stabbed his
OL,19,Fwife in the neck and had previously
OL,20,Fsubjected her to physical abuse.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
