OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1775315485
OL,3,CHusband, 51, jailed for wife's murder
OL,4,Cafter she initiated divorce proceedings
OL,6,FWest Midlands Police found Paramjit
OL,7,Fwith serious injuries at a house in
OL,8,FSwan Crescent at around 8.20am on 1
OL,9,FApril.
OL,11,FShe was confirmed dead at the scene.
OL,13,FMattu refused to give evidence and
OL,14,Fdenied murder at his trial, claiming
OL,15,Fhis wife, who had initiated divorce
OL,16,Fproceedings two months earlier, had
OL,17,Fattacked him with a knife, leading to
OL,18,Fa fatal confrontation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1775315485
OL,3,CHusband, 51, jailed for wife's murder
OL,4,Cafter she initiated divorce proceedings
OL,6,FBut jurors convicted him of murder
OL,7,Flast week after retiring for just one
OL,8,Fhour and 18 minutes.
OL,10,FPassing a life sentence at
OL,11,FWolverhampton Crown Court on Thursday,
OL,12,FJudge John Butterfield KC said he
OL,13,Fbelieved two specific previous
OL,14,Fincidents of violence before the
OL,15,Fkilling were "the tip of the iceberg"
OL,16,Famid a background of repeated assaults.
OL,18,FThe judge also said it was plausible
OL,19,Fthat a knife was placed at the scene
OL,20,Fso Mattu could later claim he had been
OL,21,Fattacked.
OL,26,@wD@NOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
