CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1775315485
OL,3,CHusband, 51, jailed for wife's murder
OL,4,Cafter she initiated divorce proceedings
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination showed that
OL,7,FMs Kaur, who was also known as Soni,
OL,8,Fdied from pressure to the neck, rather
OL,9,Fthan stab injuries believed to have
OL,10,Fbeen inflicted while she was
OL,11,Funconscious.
OL,13,FA trial was told that she was in the
OL,14,Fprocess of leaving Mattu, who had
OL,15,Fpreviously slapped her across the
OL,16,Fface, twisted her leg, broken her
OL,17,Fphone and grabbed her by the throat.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
