OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1775315485
OL,3,CHusband, 51, jailed for wife's murder
OL,4,Cafter she initiated divorce proceedings
OL,6,FIt is believed she briefly moved out
OL,7,Fof the marital home late in 2024 but
OL,8,Ftemporarily returned after Mattu
OL,9,Fexpressed suicidal feelings.
OL,11,FJudge Butterfield told Mattu: "You
OL,12,Fwere thoroughly manipulating her even
OL,13,Fwhen she had separated from you.
OL,15,F"You played on her emotions and ramped
OL,16,Fup the pressure to remain married to
OL,17,Fyou."
OL,19,FThe judge added that the previous
OL,20,Fincidents of violence and coercion
OL,21,Fwere aggravating factors in the case.
OL,26,@sD@_OUwD@AOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1775315485
OL,3,CHusband, 51, jailed for wife's murder
OL,4,Cafter she initiated divorce proceedings
OL,6,F"Many seconds of strangulation are not
OL,7,Fsensibly consistent with anything less
OL,8,Fthan an intention to kill," the judge
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe judge also said he believed the
OL,12,Fknife injuries were inflicted when the
OL,13,Fvictim was "at least unconscious and,
OL,14,Fin reality, close to death".
OL,16,FOffering mitigation for Mattu, Amjad
OL,17,FMalik KC, said the killing was a
OL,18,F"spontaneous act of violence" but
OL,19,Faccepted the jury had "very, very
OL,20,Fquickly" decided Mattu acted in anger.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@[O]uD@LOUvD@[O]zD@AOUzD@]O]{D@
