OL,3,CHusband, 51, jailed for wife's murder
OL,4,Cafter she initiated divorce proceedings
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read for
OL,7,Fthe court record by prosecution
OL,8,Fbarrister Jonathan Barker, the
OL,9,Fvictim's brother said: "My sister was
OL,10,Fvery hard-working. My sister was kind
OL,11,Fand charitable.
OL,13,F"She would give to people who needed
OL,14,Fit. Paramjit was very caring and was
OL,15,Falways there when we as a family
OL,16,Fneeded her.
OL,18,F"We all went to her for advice and as
OL,19,Fthe person to talk to."
OL,26,@qD@XOUuD@AOUzD@AOU{D@WO]
